{"tid":1331039,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【一毛全攻略】一分鐘熟知一毛手段、應對以及撚毛方法","createTime":"2019-07-18T19:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:29:26.000Z","uid":58841,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3e98bcafc937bf6d143c767c9c646344ea010257","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:53:46.000Z","msg":"今次就唔開係時事台了，轉開學術台<br />\n小弟自12年開始同五毛互相攻擊，其中有幾個殺到仇家咁<br />\n有個直頭係KMT黨員黎<br />\n因為佢地只會藍綠互片搞台灣，所以好少會搞著我<br />\n不過我觀察左連登一段時間，原來手段都係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一毛手法：</strong><br />\n1.一邊做正方，一邊做反方互屌，屌到咁上下就會有傻仔加入<br />\n例如琴晚我發現有唔少一毛扮熱狗，得罪講句以熱狗煩膠個性，係肯定咬住你唔放<br />\n<br />\n2.推舊POST上水，搞到你地失焦<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6uCrrwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uCrrwW.jpg&h=dd4b5040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.FAKE NEWS 「我個FD話」「聽人講」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VFp1Bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VFp1Bb.jpg&h=1743530f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.不停開新聞POST洗底<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/jJFXxWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJFXxWL.jpg&h=8f4850cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.長期覆COMMENT只係打表情，又或者得張圖<br />\n我有幾個長期跟蹤既一毛，高級一毛係甚少開POST<br />\n但係好多時會係你POST出現<br />\n<br />\n6.表面負面撚實際上曲線讚美，唔會見到佢地直接屌中共<br />\n<br />\n<strong>應對方法：</strong><br />\n1.唔好回覆由得個POST沉，一毛不停推POST去到咁上下就會自動收皮<br />\n<br />\n2.唔好睇正負評，連登太多羊仔跟住人行<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考，切忌跟風</span>。你只要開POST發表意見，變相係助攻帶風向<br />\n<br />\n4.不停推應該推既POST 例如721<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當然，呢D只係佢地招數，唔好諗住捉一毛<br />\n分分鐘捉錯人，只作參考用途</span><br />\n<br />\n當然，咁唔可能得個守架嘛<br />\n等到你開始分到一毛啦，就可以進行反擊<br />\n以下方法慎用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>反擊操作：</strong><br />\n1.引戰POST，釣魚<br />\n最佳例子：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1330754/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1330754/page/1</a><br />\n入面就有幾隻一毛上水係度互相打飛機<br />\n想學人釣魚之前一定要熟知一毛同埋睇多D呢類POST<br />\n一個唔該就俾一毛騎劫風向<br />\n例如PTT就好撚多釣魚文值得學習<br />\n<br />\n2.先發制人<br />\n例如呢篇：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1330511/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1330511/page/1</a><br />\n其實呢條橋前幾日已經有連登仔提過，只不過俾我撈返上水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1317680/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1317680/page/1</a><br />\n風向一旦成功帶走，一毛只可以鳩推POST分散版面焦點<br />\n<br />\n3.假設好不幸咁俾一毛帶風向，咁就要盡快出POST騎劫返轉頭<br />\n騎唔到至少都要55開，琴日只係得TVB SOURCE同陳雲就洗到成個版面都係<br />\n呢種情況下標題好重要，點落法自行參透<br />\n<br />\n4.選擇適當戰場，即係話，如果你想屌柒一毛<br />\n就要睇係咩POST入面，如果係垃圾POST膠POST既就唔好同佢嘈即刻BLOCK＋冷處理<br />\n如果係<span style=\"color: red;\">重要POST</span>就屌到佢老母都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過同一毛嘈到成千個COMMENT<br />\n不過一毛都唔係蠢，佢唔會選擇係重要POST同你嘈<br />\n<br />\n反擊係要搞到中聯辦盤棋散撚哂，同埋要比朝早既人睇到發生咩事<br />\n其實正常都知深夜時間根本唔會有新鮮野出黎<br />\n所以都只係攻防戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我期待一毛會有咩新招等住我去拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b89fe8cd239f5715560e9b9fba52576a61beea","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:56:10.000Z","msg":"利申：入面既相同LINK唔代表就係一毛，我只係拎黎做例子"},{"pid":"d25cc7a77433d66c3402747a3800efb6cdc79510","tid":1331039,"uid":198343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:59:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2aec770113041cdf2af85cf17a0438b7c9be4c19","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:00:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>關於釣魚文：</strong><br />\n樓主通常會開個好撚偏頗既標題同內文<br />\n然後嘈到一半就會人間蒸發<br />\n留低班人係度互屌<br />\n就我睇其實連登仲停留係釣魚文BB班階段"},{"pid":"82c5b7416554855edc12263d247cb6136dfc6d35","tid":1331039,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:01:55.000Z","msg":"［請立即宣傳7.21 勿再爲連儂牆開post］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331027</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5388c882dab26323e38626999fafadfb992779c7","tid":1331039,"uid":263973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:31:22.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"949e5ae33cce66bc27a86ef4aa8cb6f4225aa4e8","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T21:51:31.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"92b25ccf84b3790f547f95523142a1d8813be92a","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c90b1b5543219bedb77e7abda4799f17bde0b5d8","tid":1331039,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a47b04ac73cb19d1978d11f143bca8e18db3e04","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"留意<br />\n有一毛帶風向叫人捉鬼<br />\n條友我追蹤開遮住名先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lohv2F8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLohv2F8.png&h=c5833777&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b97f20b850a426c105ed9e804f854ebda1e5eb90","tid":1331039,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:27:25.000Z","msg":"巴打開既推左先睇"},{"pid":"a1508e412758d0a721c1ad65d715a32d88b65a25","tid":1331039,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:29:42.000Z","msg":"有啲on9 post 叫左唔好覆下面仲要覆既人其實係想點<br />\n一毛一向都係冷處理 有用po就繼續同佢鬥推<br />\n垃圾po就唔洗覆唔洗理"},{"pid":"b5316049d76232fc8b23e75da7e56092595417c6","tid":1331039,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:30:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28767361f628c08e130edad821ff65992ca782fb","tid":1331039,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"啱。<br />\n有需要就負評，上一頁，其實就已經夠。"},{"pid":"51b8a5a5a23a267edf388e96009a39527ba90036","tid":1331039,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:53:08.000Z","msg":"個post幾有用<br />\n<br />\nBookmark先"},{"pid":"68fdaad45cbe4ed198c07824a50f1ca10cb4c241","tid":1331039,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:54:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bd774588815f1286a4f1d5446506685b2cd1856b","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:58:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>如何對付不斷推POST既一毛撚屌：</strong><br />\n簡單黎講，就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">記低ID</span><br />\n係同一個POST入面，ID重覆頻率越高代表一毛可能性越大<br />\n至於個POST ID個個唔同咁點呀？<br />\n咁就將焦點擺落樓主度，睇佢D POST/一毛POST再計重覆頻率<br />\n呢招其實好撚豬，因為係變相自爆<br />\n連登有幾個高級一毛我長期跟開<br />\n佢地係唔會經常性係一毛POST出現"},{"pid":"2be2abb934f193f508dcc655bef82daeb3a4b0cd","tid":1331039,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:05:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7006fd7f7709f1e69a7ed7d427ea2a6c3c83d3d7","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:32:00.000Z","msg":"唔知點解突然有傻仔見人係P牌同空AC就屌係鬼<br />\n我想問你咁撚無腦同藍絲有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日開POST唔代表係鬼AC好無<br />\n都有高級一毛好識玩一日開幾十個POST黎洗地<br />\n即係同第四點相似呀<br />\n起底係俾你知道佢開POST通常係咩取向<br />\n唔係話少開POST＝鬼<br />\n再講唔好低估一毛流動性<br />\n醒少少啦"},{"pid":"575cbd0188662bf4ca32aa12d87969a632b932c4","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解突然有傻仔見人係P牌同空AC就屌係鬼<br />\n我想問你咁撚無腦同藍絲有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日開POST唔代表<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>係鬼AC好無<br />\n都有高級一毛好識玩一日開幾十個POST黎洗地<br />\n即係同第四點相似呀<br />\n起底係俾你知道佢開POST通常係咩取向<br />\n唔係話少開POST＝鬼<br />\n再講唔好低估一毛流動性<br />\n醒少少啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0a323c513f07083b79dc095d0bbe79be00236566","tid":1331039,"uid":274573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:54:25.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔係好分到<br />\n但推"},{"pid":"322ea22c2b6102f8b1deed705ce6da031887e192","tid":1331039,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a323c513f07083b79dc095d0bbe79be00236566","tid":1331039,"uid":274573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:54:25.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔係好分到<br />\n但推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:57:20.000Z","msg":"係比較難分+好易誤中副車<br />\n有啲揚哂都仲繼續出黎個啲就柒啲<br />\n西環冇比新ac佢"},{"pid":"099306fe7e016c66970c4053fb37d4e70898e582","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a323c513f07083b79dc095d0bbe79be00236566","tid":1331039,"uid":274573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:54:25.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔係好分到<br />\n但推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:01:36.000Z","msg":"睇得多你就識分"},{"pid":"79aa2ee393815d63342417e6951b0afe998528ca","tid":1331039,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"bfc616cdaca80e1f9c723beaf3fa1696e58fc7d7","tid":1331039,"uid":235711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"push"}]}